Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真歷71年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日後被稱為第三銀河帝國起源的那一年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類將自己的生存領域向著地球外推進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere的開發加速了宇宙探索的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在宇宙人口已經佔總人口的七成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是迪歐爾第一殖民衛星Module 77 請報上船籍
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是GS2776第21號航班 請求入港許可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船籍確認 准許入港
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲森學園的轉校生2名 沒有問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 確認無誤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝水咽下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出男子氣概！ 晴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸啊 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負還很難說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦 時縞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣決出勝負啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早著呢早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是熱鬧非凡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在用速食比賽來爭奪操場的使用權
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經高中生了還要搶操場…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼和平 不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爭點氣啊 晴人
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}還想踢足球的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這得檢討一下了
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}拜託你爭點氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不願意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啦 猜拳輸了任人魚肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗家之犬自此與勝無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無緣無緣 晴人對勝負完全沒有想法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想被穿著奇怪T恤的人說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毬惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是翔子你啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到迪歐爾Module 77
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的Module天氣也很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉校生不是兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平過頭了 迪歐爾這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由多爾希亞和ARUS兩國的勢力平衡來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩國的特徵就是 通過「他國國際間條約」不斷擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我一下考試範圍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟學校建成才三年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又懶得跑回地球去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所學校不是很漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計佈局很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽說那個傳說中的祠堂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 據說肯定能兩情相悅
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.80,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sphere的建造～各國的代表性Dyson Sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.80,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽說那個傳說中的話題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.80,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 肯定是兩情相悅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.80,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們聽說了嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多爾希亞軍又要進行邊界劃定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正最後又是咱們這邊花錢消災吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來這套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真是不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嘛 比起建立軍隊省錢多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為老說這種話這個國家才會沒落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 晴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 不去跟翔子告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.54,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz341.565\pos(452,219)}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.54,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz340.388\pos(334,576)}沒什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.54,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz339.35\pos(345,615)}什麼事都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 什麼事都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.88,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被其他人搶走的話就哭也來不及啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始你就盯著我這邊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有事 給我看下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有啦 真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此就讓我看下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NICE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我啊 不還回來我就跟你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就老實回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼盯著這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你不說話的時候很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 只是不說話的時候而已啦 可以說是限定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎 說話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是說不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…漂亮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那也不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬冢前輩還真是三句話不離錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是打算總有一天成為世界首富呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想遠大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話希望能給我們帶下路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件裙子很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事 我在和她說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是邀請她去舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無論何時都不忘禮儀主義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與當地人的接觸要縮小至最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你知道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴灑裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以13M為單位擺放的噴灑裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座建築前時變成了間隔12.5M
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶來看教室的座位數是40
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生數有480人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這座建築物是以一般的積層構造法建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從承重來看無法承受多餘的設施人員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推導出來的結論就是 建築物的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名不虛傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是幾年級的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉校生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人 你是心意不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的比賽啊 你根本沒認真想過要贏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我覺得世界如果沒有勝負之爭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操場也是 大家對半平分就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無論火腿煎蛋還是喜歡的女人 都會用刀切成兩半嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福是沒法平分的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是幾年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 別過來 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不戰鬥 對方打過來的話你又該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑嘻嘻地將勝利拱手相讓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓步的話就只能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海老師 你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學有補習 但她還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個藝人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊 是我交代錯時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 火腿煎蛋是從蛋白開始吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了火腿煎蛋的重點是火腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火腿才是重點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被推倒的是晴人才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人明明說的是好事嘛 完全沒錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在替我生氣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 多虧你我平靜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因為我們是朋友嘛 可晴人你又不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸要保持在最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通了 門要開了
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.55,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓這份戀情實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人也要許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這裡是告白就一定會兩情相悅的傳說中的祠堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛建成三年的學校怎麼可能會有傳說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-ELF發來電文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蝙蝠 飛向 陰沉的天空」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大佐的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本國發信「Operation Virgin Road」開始
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,662)}   BLESS     ALEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮光耀我 艾蓮陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BUFFET 一號機 推進器啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點低呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他國家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多爾希亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在往哪飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多爾希亞的型號NW507BE BUFFET有人機…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快點進校舍 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 到底搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認多爾希亞方面艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本國請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 通訊無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼多爾希亞軍會打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟本國聯繫不上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說正在被轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐爾明明是中立國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動Valvrave吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負得起責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名不虛傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃獨食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車裡面還有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子 快回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 你們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 翔子 不是捉迷藏的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來 翔子 翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 晴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人同學 已經！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會走的 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須接受 她已經死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人 很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們來之前還是等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒 不可原諒 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出來了 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形機？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 前方發現一級作戰目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群小鬼 失敗了嗎 所以我才說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去將駕駛員分離出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 動起來啊 你不是機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為翔子報仇啊 求你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 動起來啊 快動…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.41,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.983\pos(605,251)}為了啟動Valvrave 請回答以下問題
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.41,barkeitai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.757\pos(658,495)}要放棄做人嗎 YES/NO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就… 開始擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在收集關於迪歐爾遭到多爾希亞軍攻擊的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府也正在應對中
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被攻打著呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪歐爾的機體嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.18,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多爾希亞軍的BUFFET
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去不就好了
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.81,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說這邊是迪歐爾的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有武器嗎 你不是兵器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.82,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.82,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰在搭乘著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.36,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.03,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.16,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍回去啊快揍回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.54,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在援軍來之前挺住啊
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.50,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.46,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.67,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去根本贏不了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.75,bar2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法報仇 就這麼死去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 翔子 我又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒認真想過要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓步的話 就只有戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓步… 所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化了？ 顏色和力量都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種連戰爭都不懂的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些光是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 到底是什麼光啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.97,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.09,bar1,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.30,bar1,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.14,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,對手是軍人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.80,bar2,,0000,0000,0000,,網上的新聞我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.81,bar2,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的性能差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.89,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.60,bar1,,0000,0000,0000,,那個機器人到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.14,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,那機器人是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.31,bar1,,0000,0000,0000,,機器人這個說法並不準確
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.39,bar2,,0000,0000,0000,,那是軍用機？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.23,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.52,bar2,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐爾的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.60,bar1,,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.77,bar3,,0000,0000,0000,,照片上傳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.06,bar2,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鄰班的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那孩子啊 就是早上那個人
